{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_6_level_main_06-15_end","storyGroup":"main_6","storySort":25,"storyDependence":"main_6_level_main_06-14_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"6-17","storyName":"冬逝","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"霜星永远地闭上了双眼。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_06-15_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_06-15","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":24,"next":26,"characters":["霜星","煌","阿米娅"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"第三关（后）","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":2},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bottlebroken","id":3},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/69/Avg_avg_6_9.png","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":5},{"type":"character","id":6},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"15","block":"false","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"4","id":8},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"image","fadetime":"0","id":10},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":11},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_bg_bg_undergroud_f.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":12},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":13},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"碎了......吗。","id":15,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"老爷子从某个巫师那里求得这样东西......说是能维持住我的性命。","id":16,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"连一场战斗都没撑过去，呵呵，终归，还是假货。","id":17,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"也许就像我们父女一样......？和现在的，荒诞的整合运动......也一样。","id":18,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","text":"","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"唔！","id":20,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/83/Avg_char_017_homura_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"呃......","id":21,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/83/Avg_char_017_homura_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"咳，咳......煌！","id":23,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","text":"","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"寒流已经......消散了。","id":25,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/83/Avg_char_017_homura_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"我没事！阿米娅，快，去看看那只白兔子！","id":26,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/83/Avg_char_017_homura_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"赢得漂亮，罗德岛。","id":28,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我的兄弟姐妹们......我让他们白白死去了。","id":29,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我们什么都没做到。","id":30,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我的生命......一点价值都没有。","id":31,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"33","text":"他们是因为你的理念而追随你的。"}},"values":[],"id":32},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":33},{"type":"character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","text":"","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"......","id":35,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/83/Avg_char_017_homura_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#7","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我的死......不值得任何人久留。","id":37,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6c/Avg_char_1505_frstar_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"去救你们还能救的人吧。赶快。","id":39,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"快去。","id":40,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"无论是阻止那些穿雨衣的，还是去追杀梅菲斯特，还是收容那些无处可去的感染者......","id":41,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"去吧。去做有价值的事。","id":42,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":44,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"博士......","id":45,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"47","text":"我留下。"},"2":{"id":"47","text":"你去吧。"}},"values":[],"id":46},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":47,"end":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我知道了。","id":48,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"博士，请告诉霜星小姐那句话。","id":49,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......拜托你。","id":50,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":51},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":52},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$frostnovadie_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_frostnovadie_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1.5","id":53,"musicid":0},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/4d/Avg_avg_6_10.png","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":54},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":55},{"type":"character","id":56},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"真是只......天真的兔子。","id":58,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"很像啊。和当时的塔露拉，很像。","id":59,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"在死前能看到这样的人，这样坚定地去实现理想的人......","id":60,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":61},{"type":"character","id":62},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"64","text":"说好的责任呢？！"},"2":{"id":"64","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"64","text":"不是答应说要加入罗德岛的吗？"}},"values":[],"id":63},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":64,"end":82},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"凭你的头脑，应该也考虑到这点了吧？","id":66,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"坏人也要有坏人该有的样子。我对自己应得的结局毫无怨言。","id":67,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我伤害了你们，我和整合运动把目标对准了无辜的龙门人，一手促成了乌萨斯感染者的黑暗未来，这样的人根本没资格去罗德岛。","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我的兄弟姐妹......这些傻子，一定是想着让我活着吧？","id":69,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"本以为哪怕这一次我死去了，这些傻子也能因此得到个允许他们活下去的地方。","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"没有，并没有。他们死了。为了保护我这个本来就没多少时间的人。","id":71,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我不甘心。我们的性命全都被人利用了。","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我不甘心......这最后一刻的生命，这一点不属于我，这是他们所有人用血去换来的！","id":73,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"这一点点生命.......我必须交给值得信任的人。","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"谢谢你。","id":75,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":".......啊......即使活下来了，又有哪里可去呢？","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我们本就没有其它地方可去。我们熟悉的从来就只有那片雪原而已。","id":77,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"龙门并不是乌萨斯。渴望着拯救同胞和感染者，想要去找一处又温暖，又有粮食，还有住处的地方......","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"不该是龙门。自一开始，就不该是龙门。龙门的市民也在苦苦寻求自己的生活。","id":79,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我们唯一该回去的，就只有乌萨斯......我们的祖国......","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"雪......静静的河水......摇曳的松林......碧绿的苔衣......","id":81,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"这片大地，多么美好啊......","id":82,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":83},{"type":"character","id":84},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"86","text":"所以，你认为塔露拉是操纵了这一切的人。"}},"values":[],"id":85},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":86,"end":95},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"......如果我猜的没错......阴谋已经蓄势待发。","id":88,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"就算博卓卡斯替老爷子能拖上一时，塔露拉既然敢这样谋划，就一定有对付他的办法。","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"龙门没有出手的机会......而乌萨斯也会袖手旁观。","id":90,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"但你们还在，感染者还有机会。哪怕只有一点点——","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"——去毁掉现在的塔露拉。中止她的疯狂，不要让整合运动再吞噬更多感染者了。整合运动不需要塔露拉，任何一个塔露拉都不需要......","id":92,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"或者......","id":93,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"......我的一点点私心。去拯救她。不。去帮助她。和我们那无数的感染者同胞一起......","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"那个真正的......走在泥泞土地上的......塔露拉......","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":96},{"type":"character","id":97},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"99","text":"霜星小姐？"}},"values":[],"id":98},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":99,"end":101},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"你......说。","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":102},{"type":"character","id":103},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"105","text":"我认为你父亲是真的爱你的。"}},"values":[],"id":104},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":105},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"107","text":"就像你记得你的亲生父母为你而死。"}},"values":[],"id":106},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":107},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"109","text":"你清楚地记着你父亲为你所做的一切。"}},"values":[],"id":108},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":109,"end":114},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"......","id":111,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我又怎么会不知道呢？只是，我要死在他之前了。","id":112,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"如果他从来没捡到我，那会有多好。那样，他就不会因我感到痛苦。","id":113,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"他已经受了那么多的苦......","id":114,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":115},{"type":"character","id":116},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"118","text":"正因为他受过很多苦，所以他才珍惜你。"}},"values":[],"id":117},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":118,"end":126},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"呵呵......","id":120,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"......博士。","id":121,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我可以这么叫你吧？","id":122,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"罗德岛的博士。在这片大地上，选择也许没有意义。","id":123,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"即使这样，即使结果没有区别......我也想自己去选。我做出选择了。","id":124,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"用我自己的手......去擦拭我结出的果。","id":125,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"text","text":"霜星的手指摸索着你的面庞。","id":126,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":127},{"type":"character","id":128},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"130","text":"......你的手指，是暖的？"}},"values":[],"id":129},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":130,"end":133},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"奇怪。你的脸......很冰。","id":132,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我的体温......没有那么低了？","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":134},{"type":"character","id":135},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"137","text":"是。你的病征消失了。"},"2":{"id":"137","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"137","text":"很温暖，霜星。"}},"values":[],"id":136},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":137},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"......在死前......我终于又和人相碰了。","id":139,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"141","text":"霜星，阿米娅和我都希望你加入罗德岛。"}},"values":[],"id":140},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我真有这种资格？","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"144","text":"仅仅是普通地死去，就没有时间再去改正错误。"}},"values":[],"id":143},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":144,"end":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"......不给出答复是不礼貌的。","id":145,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"告诉阿米娅，Dr.{@nickname}......","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"在这片大地上，仅凭一个人，是什么也做不到的。","id":147,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_char_1505_frstar_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":148},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/82/Avg_avg_6_10_2.png","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":149},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":150},{"type":"character","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"但她绝对不是一个人。","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"现在开始，我在你身边。我在你们身边。","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我......愿意加入罗德岛。","id":154},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"156","text":"谢谢你。"}},"values":[],"id":155},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"不。是我......谢谢你。","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"你的眼神......和我一位旧识，很像。","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我遇见过一个男孩，他说他的哥哥宁愿上绞架也不愿改变观点去迎合敌人的宽恕......","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"所以他要走过雪原，他要踏遍乌萨斯.......所以他没有和我们一起走。","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"我以为那已经是我见过最理想化的人了。","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"只是，你和阿米娅让我觉得……也许理想也可以成为一种信念。","id":162},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"164","text":"罗德岛就是为了共同的信念而战的。"}},"values":[],"id":163},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":164,"end":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"原本整合运动......也是一样的。","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"真像啊。","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"你的眼神，和那个孩子，真的很像。","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"只不过，你没他那么坚定，但却比他......温柔太多了。","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"放手吧。兄弟姐妹们在等我。","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"......父亲......我真是个傻子。","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"原谅我吧。","id":171,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":172},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":173},{"type":"image","fadetime":"0","id":174},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":175},{"type":"dialog","id":176},{"type":"character","id":177},{"type":"background","id":178},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":179},{"type":"text","text":"她滑落下去。","id":180},{"type":"text","text":"她的嘴角上扬，高傲得像是依然还活着一般。","id":181},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":182},{"type":"dialog","id":183},{"type":"blocker","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":184},{"type":"image","id":185}],"characters":["霜星","煌","阿米娅"]}